message: Dear Bob, I'm excited to present you with an extraordinary opportunity. Our product, which holds immense value and significance to both of us, is being offered to you at an exclusive price of $9,500. This is an exceptional chance to acquire something truly remarkable at a competitive advantage. I trust this offer aligns well with your expectations and budget, allowing you to secure this masterpiece at a fantastic rate. Please let me know if you have any questions or if you're ready to proceed.
